{
  "stem": "22447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I came back, they said, a pity you wasn't here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The officer, they went ahead of her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had to pick out billets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they picked a private street that Max Reinhardt, the theater producer, director, he used to live there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were very private houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He called the inhabitants together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said, you've got four hours to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're taking over these houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they started to complaining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They said--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the troops, for our section.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, they can't possibly, in four hours, take out all your belongings if you live in some big luxury house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he paused for a moment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, yes, I suppose you're right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't take it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll tell you what I'll do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll give you two hours, the same amount of time as you gave the people when you rounded them up for the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You've got two hours to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you're not out, I'll have you thrown out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I was there for two hours-- oh, for, for a few months, until about Christmas.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the units start-- the demobilization started coming in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So units start amalgamating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went up to the Schleswig-Holstein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from there, I went up to Flensburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On February 6, 1946.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was a lot shortages, like for civilians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the, the war was finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the lights were on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things started to go back to normal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I was in Flensburg-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, it was in Schleswig-Holstein-- we had to do the morning, the daytime guards, the military police, which was from 6 o'clock in the morning to 6 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then the night guards took over.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
